Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡真是大到感覺會迷路的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但這別墅也太高級了吧 竟然連溫泉都有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 竟然拿來辦合宿 感覺有點浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡本來是我曾祖母在住的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是後來才改建成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽說發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎? 一臉心事重重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在 正值暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我深信我們可以改變過去和未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Hope to be with you even after rebirth......Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}願即使在我們重生之後 也能與你在一起.....即使在重生之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今日が過去に変わる事で　明日が近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日成為過去 明日隨之到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如此理所當然的事 心卻為此留下了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}將那天所見到的『世界』 再一次呈現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}若有朝一日能夠實現的話 便已再無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不論受到誰 彷彿已無可能性般的冷嘲熱諷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}次の君に逢える日まで　繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}直到能遇見下一個你之前 那反覆流轉的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}たとえ　どんな道でも　決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}無論前方是怎樣的道路　絕對 絕對 不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}『あした、またね。』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}『明天，再見吧。』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}その『未来』を　いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}為了不再失去那『未來』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}終わりのない始まり　今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那沒有盡頭的開端　現在 想和你 進入夢鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}請不要放開 那牽著的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我深信我們可以改變過去和未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}願即使在我們重生之後 也能與你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}I'm confident we can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我深信我們可以改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&30&\pos(492,872)\fad (300,300)}第13話 『尋找失去的暑假』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯同學 帽子找到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 在桌子上找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 今天是幾號來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸? 十三號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十三...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦!? 已經十三號了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 七月十三號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}七...七月?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}花梨在暑假也會很忙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 因為有演唱會和各種活動要忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古川同學妳呢? 暑假有什麼打算嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該做什麼才好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是不該去干涉這個時間軸的事象呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是該從現在就開始關注佳織同學的一舉一動呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經不曉得 這種狀況該怎麼辦才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都來到這裡了 幹嘛還擺著那副死氣沉沉的表情啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:04:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那個...我對合宿並不是很了解...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}講是講合宿 但我們也只是很普通的出來玩而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去海邊玩啦 放個煙火 烤個肉之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像很有趣的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是些我沒體驗過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就趁這次全部體驗一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然都加入天文學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就好好地享受此時此刻的當下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把煩惱拋到九霄雲外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此時此刻的當下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼這次會來到時間偏移這麼多的時間軸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在就算想這些 也得不出什麼答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正想也想不透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那倒不如什麼都不去想 好好地享受當下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 我就好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是極樂世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}溫泉真是日本優秀的culture啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打擾了 請問方便讓我一起入浴嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 結束~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的假的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣 又是我當富豪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過話說回來 這裡好多看起來很昂貴的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這棟別墅 是曾祖母拿來放收藏品的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然她在我剛出生不久就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但聽說她是個相當古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為華宮研究所的創立者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽說她是當時少見的女性科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您的曾祖母大人是在華宮軍事工廠擔任技術開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相當優秀的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在來這裡的途中 我好像有在附近看到一間像廢棄工廠的建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 那就是曾經的軍事工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那附近人煙稀少 相當危險 請不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那裡也曾被曾祖母當作她的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽說她好像在那裡做一些奇怪的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也聽說過有人在那裡看到幽靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要去試膽啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今年我買了新泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 嗯...還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這件是從華宮同學那裡借來的 看起來會不會很奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Very sexy~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那根手指是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多說兩句好話嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't mind, don't mind~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要揍人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請不要做危險的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用這麼擔心啦 我們都不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 我四點來接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那就麻煩你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小唯 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯同學不一起去玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我有一點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看唯同學妳開心的樣子 我也很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這就是所謂的暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為 現在會因為暑假而感動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找遍全日本 大概也只有唯同學妳而已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晚上我們準備放煙火哦 妳就好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煙火 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才剛講完的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來還會下一陣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學姊 今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是 那我打電話請人來接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}　沙學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(865,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨看起來是暫時不會停了 我們換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來這麼做會比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果還是來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡就是曾經的軍事工廠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺像廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在雨停之前 我們就來exploration吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Exploration? 探險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要做太危險的事喔 不然會被作之進罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點令人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 你們真的要去喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}地下道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該是倉庫之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}入口這麼小 應該放不了太大的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真想下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要下去看看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像蠻深的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}電還通著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡會不會是防空洞之類的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個 感覺比較像研究設施之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡如果是屬於　沙家的東西的話 搞不好會藏有什麼寶藏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(605,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨好像停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得都來了 就再往裡面走一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妳是那種在恐怖電影中最早領便當的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隨便分個組 分頭去探險看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十分鐘後在入口處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒半個人在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是暑假會進行的活動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 說是應該也算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是在好什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 就進這個房間看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡是...寢室?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該說是保健室之類的地方吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種地方感覺就會有ghost跑出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好痛啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有受傷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是幽靈 真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}機會難得 就拍個照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是有帶手機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡應該沒有訊號吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦 是想說拿來當手電筒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再稍微等一下吧 搞不好等等電就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無論如何 在眼睛習慣黑暗前都別輕舉妄動會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻煩過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我現在就過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了? 發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}供電好像不太穩定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會不會是打雷造成的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:15:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}避免危險 在看不清楚路的情況下 還是別四處亂跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼? 怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個洞是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黑漆漆的 什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺都是些艱澀難懂的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是德語吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個 妳看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妳看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦? 這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏...奏啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊? 他好像失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏 奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佐佐木同學 請冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是該把他敲醒啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 現在還是別動他會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個 我們先和華宮同學他們匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡著了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這算什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該是太累了吧 竟然在這種地方睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這該不會是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過話說回來 奏在床底下做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不...不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是舊式的收音機吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦? 小佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}K...Kenny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛 原來是佳織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幽...幽靈 出...出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 剛才那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之 先和奏同學他們匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說...說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂~ 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行 完全沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該是累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Kenny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個...那張床下面有沒有什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸? 床下?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然不清楚是不是幽靈 但確實是有什麼東西在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之 先離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撒嬌也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小唯她...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}麻煩妳了 我在這裡等妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織 走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸? 我也要去喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古川唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 這裡也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡就是　沙學姊昨天說過的地方吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(728,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然說是研究設施 但這看起來根本就是下水道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我快尿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我記得應該有...吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧 佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在這裡等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給妳 用這個來照明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不進去 我是絕對不會進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點 不然要尿出來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織? 佳織!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妳終於現身啦 幽靈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就我們來看 您才是幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}華宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令人一時難以置信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 這名為AI單元的匣子 在八十年後的未來也還是個未解之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只知道它是個會對時間和空間造成影響的歐帕茲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1456,985)}OOPArt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歐帕茲?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(944,985)}OOPArt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是「用對那個時代來說不可能實現的科學技術製作出來的東西」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是從祖母那裡拿到這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還以為它只是個普通的玻璃盒而已的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還有很多問題想問妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:22:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如說像 妳現在的穿著 在妳的時代是很平常的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其他人手上拿著的閃閃發光的東西又是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 只有妳可以操作那個匣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 因為回答這些問題可能會對歷史造成影響...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}講這種話 自己聽起來都覺得有點刺耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.71,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 我只問這個就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這場戰爭 日本最後怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 連　沙學姊都在啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(868,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還比我們先找到唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是費了好大一番功夫啊 佳織又昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才真是對不起啊 我沒打算要嚇妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸? 剛才?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才那個是　沙學姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.34,0:22:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(1008,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:22:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 我們快點離開這種地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得我不是很喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思 妳們先回去找秋山同學他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們再聊幾句就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 那我們就先過去囉 先走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}華宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妳們是朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯...算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺真不錯呢 等這場戰爭結束後 我來當學校的老師好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佳織 妳差不多該醒過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學姊!? 妳什麼時候回來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回來? 我一直都待在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛理同學? 妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不喜歡這種過分的玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.95,0:24:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好像突然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.32,0:24:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個時候的事 我完全沒印象了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不覺得自己有這麼累啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Come on! 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.35,0:24:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:24:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欸? 等...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過話說回來 真是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.66,0:25:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們竟然從地下的酒窖裡跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼妳會知道那個出口啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.14,0:25:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是某人告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.18,0:25:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}某人?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就不過問了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.51,0:25:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.84,0:25:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是令人懷念啊 這位就是您的曾祖母大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.93,0:25:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和我長得一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.49,0:25:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想起了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.96,0:25:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的內濱學園 就是您的曾祖母大人所創立的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.16,0:26:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽說她因為和一位少女相遇 而大幅改變了她的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.04,0:26:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那位大人 總是將目光放往長遠的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.65,0:26:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.42,0:26:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奏 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.81,0:26:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這孩子在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.47,0:26:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 應該正在做美夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.66,0:26:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}夕暮れ　帰り道　並んで歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.66,0:26:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}與你並肩走在黃昏的歸途上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.92,0:26:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}オレンジ色の空　街を包んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.92,0:26:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}天空將街道渲染得一片橘黃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.09,0:27:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}君が好き　勇気を出して　打ちあけた気持ちに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.09,0:27:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}喜歡你 拿出勇氣 對你表明我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.31,0:27:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}君はどんな答えをくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.31,0:27:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}你會給我怎麼樣的答案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}変えられないこと　変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.90,0:27:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}想去改變那無法改變的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}失われた瞬間を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(935,1000)}{\fad(300,300)\blur3}と
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(987,1000)}{\fad(300,300)\blur3}き
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}去尋找那失去的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1095,70)}{\fad(300,300)\blur3}時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.03,0:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1140,70)}{\fad(300,300)\blur3}間
